data.description: Move right into this brick front home with 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths and 2-car garage! Updated kitchen with 42-inch espresso cabinets. Island with bar stool space. Granite countertops. Bamboo flooring on the first floor, up the stairs and in the hallway upstairs. Fireplace in the extended family room. First floor den (could be 5th bedroom) with full accessible bath adjacent. Huge master bedroom/sitting room with vaulted ceiling and luxury bath with jacuzzi/separate shower/double sinks. Contemporary lighting, doorknobs and hinges, all brushed nickel. White trim throughout. Full basement with deep pour, 9-foot ceiling and rough-in plumbing! Huge lot with paver brick patio! Home in good condition but being conveyed "As-Is". Estate Sale.
